column100:
Hi!  
 We are a modern Chinese restaurant and cocktail bar and we are looking for a dishwasher/cleaner for immediate employment.  
 Workplace is in our very popular restaurant located in the heart of Copenhagen's bar and restaurant area called Meatpacking district and work duties include the following: 
 - Dishwashing using machine 
 - Putting back of items back to the same place 
 - Clearing of rubbish 
 - General cleaning of premise 
 - Sweeping / Mopping 
   
 We offer  
 Negotiable salary depending on skills   
 A fast-paced work with room to grow  
 Friendly and international working environment  
 Staff meals 
 Housing if needed 
   
 We require 
 EU citizenship 
 Reliable and punctual work attitude 
 Willingness to work both evenings and weekends  
 Basic English skills 
   
 If you are interested then don't hesitate to contact us! Please write " Dishwasher " in the title field and send your application and a recent photo to info@magasasa.dk 
 Looking forward to hearing from you  
 Magasasa
